Class ClarifaiService.ClarifaiPutImagesInModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<Sandwich,Void,clarifai2.api.ClarifaiResponse<List<clarifai2.dto.input.ClarifaiInput>>>
      • com.learning.sandwich.sandy.service.ClarifaiService.ClarifaiPutImagesInModel
  • Enclosing class:
    ClarifaiService

    public static class ClarifaiService.ClarifaiPutImagesInModel
extends AsyncTask<Sandwich,Void,clarifai2.api.ClarifaiResponse<List<clarifai2.dto.input.ClarifaiInput>>>
    This class calls an asynchronous method that loads pictures into a given concept in Clarifai. It's onPostExecuteMethod invokes a subsequent asynchronous task that creates a model around those ages, and that class's onPostExecute invokes the final asynchronous task in the chain, which trains the model.
